%F A214526 For n > 1, a(n) = layer(n) + abs(((n-1) mod (2*layer(n)) - layer(n))) (conjectured) where layer(n) = ceiling(0.5*sqrt(n) - 0.5). - _Karl R. Stephan_, Jan 26 2018
